        "class": "ital",
        "text": "good",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Master, etc., and the reply of Jesus to him: why callest thou me good? but he agrees with Mt. in omitting some vivid traits found in Mk.: the placing of the incident (“going forth into the way”), the action of the man as he approached Jesus (",
        "children": []
